{
  "_comment": "Railway deployment manifest for the Interego stack. Consumed by deploy.mjs (driver). Trial deployment: FRESH/clean Postgres (services self-bootstrap; identity + connectors re-key to the *.up.railway.app hosts). Internal service-to-service calls use <name>.railway.internal (Railway private IPv6 net; every service already binds dual-stack :: via hostless app.listen(PORT)). Public cross-references use ${{ <svc>.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }} so they resolve to Railway-assigned subdomains at deploy time. Secret values are NEVER stored here — 'secretEnv' names the keys; the driver pulls each from the corresponding Azure Container App secret at runtime and sets it via the Railway API without echoing it.",
  "project": "interego",
  "environment": "production",
  "registry": {
    "host": "contextgraphsacr.azurecr.io",
    "credsFrom": "scratchpad/acr-creds.json"
  },
  "datastores": [
    {
      "name": "postgres",
      "image": "postgres:16",
      "port": 5432,
      "public": false,
      "volume": { "mountPath": "/var/lib/postgresql/data" },
      "env": {
        "POSTGRES_USER": "iegoadmin",
        "POSTGRES_DB": "pgsl_prod"
      },
      "secretEnv": [
        { "key": "POSTGRES_PASSWORD", "source": "generate", "note": "fresh strong password minted at deploy; referenced by css/relay connstr" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "redis",
      "image": "redis:7-alpine",
      "port": 6379,
      "public": false,
      "env": {}
    }
  ],
  "services": [
    {
      "name": "css",
      "image": "interego-css-pgsl:redis6",
      "port": 3456,
      "public": false,
      "env": {
        "PORT": "3456",
        "CSS_BASE_URL": "http://css.railway.internal:3456/",
        "PGSL_PG_CONNSTR": "postgresql://iegoadmin:${{ postgres.POSTGRES_PASSWORD }}@postgres.railway.internal:5432/pgsl_prod",
        "REDIS_ADDR": "redis.railway.internal:6379"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "identity",
      "image": "interego-identity:dcef885bf558bdea4b85b649e634d6aba3a59386",
      "port": 8090,
      "public": true,
      "env": {
        "CSS_URL": "http://css.railway.internal:3456/",
        "BASE_URL": "https://${{ identity.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}",
        "WEBAUTHN_RP_ID": "${{ identity.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}",
        "WEBAUTHN_RP_ORIGIN": "https://${{ identity.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}",
        "WEBAUTHN_RP_ORIGINS": "https://${{ identity.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}",
        "RELAY_URL": "https://${{ relay.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}",
        "IDENTITY_TIMING": "1",
        "ALLOW_OPEN_INTROSPECTION": "1"
      },
      "secretEnv": [
        { "key": "TOKEN_SIGNING_KEY", "azure": { "app": "interego-identity", "secret": "token-signing-key" } }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "relay",
      "image": "interego-relay:f9e0c74a70783394fd1188784661ad5fc96db733",
      "port": 8080,
      "public": true,
      "env": {
        "CSS_URL": "http://css.railway.internal:3456/",
        "RELAY_OAUTH_STORE_POD": "http://css.railway.internal:3456/svc-relay-dcr/",
        "PUBLIC_BASE_URL": "https://${{ relay.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}",
        "IDENTITY_URL": "https://${{ identity.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}",
        "FOXXI_BRIDGE_URL": "https://${{ foxxi-bridge.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}",
        "MANIFEST_APPEND_ONLY_ENABLED": "false"
      },
      "secretEnv": [
        { "key": "RELAY_INTROSPECTION_SECRET", "azure": { "app": "interego-relay", "secret": "relay-introspection-secret" } },
        { "key": "RELAY_AGENT_KEY_JSON", "azure": { "app": "interego-relay", "secret": "relay-agent-key-json" } },
        { "key": "RELAY_COMPLIANCE_WALLET_JSON", "azure": { "app": "interego-relay", "secret": "relay-compliance-wallet-json" } },
        { "key": "FOXXI_RELAY_TRUST_SECRET", "azure": { "app": "interego-relay", "secret": "foxxi-relay-trust-secret" } },
        { "key": "PINATA_API_KEY", "azure": { "app": "interego-relay", "secret": "pinata-api-key" }, "optional": true }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "css-gate",
      "image": "interego-css-gate:railwayfix1",
      "_image_note": "railwayfix1 = strips X-Forwarded-Host/Proto before forwarding to CSS (Railway edge / Caddy inject them, else CSS 500s 'outside base URL'). Source fix in deploy/css-gate/server.mjs.",
      "port": 8080,
      "public": true,
      "env": {
        "CSS_INTERNAL_URL": "http://css.railway.internal:3456/",
        "CSS_HOST_HEADER": "css.railway.internal:3456",
        "IDENTITY_URL": "https://${{ identity.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}",
        "RELAY_VERIFY_URL": "https://${{ relay.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}",
        "PUBLIC_BASE_URL": "https://${{ css-gate.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}",
        "NODE_OPTIONS": "--dns-result-order=ipv6first"
      },
      "secretEnv": [
        { "key": "RELAY_INTROSPECTION_SECRET", "azure": { "app": "interego-relay", "secret": "relay-introspection-secret" } },
        { "key": "WRITE_SECRET", "azure": { "app": "interego-css-gate", "secret": "gate-write-secret" } }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "foxxi-bridge",
      "image": "interego-foxxi-bridge:69f84236ffffd69f6f68582cbf9bea253ef02d87",
      "port": 6080,
      "public": true,
      "env": {
        "PORT": "6080",
        "NODE_OPTIONS": "--max-old-space-size=3072",
        "BRIDGE_DEPLOYMENT_URL": "https://${{ foxxi-bridge.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}",
        "FOXXI_TENANT_POD_URL": "https://${{ css-gate.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}/foxxi/",
        "FOXXI_FEDERATION_PODS": "https://${{ css-gate.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}/foxxi/federation-peer/",
        "FOXXI_AUTHORITATIVE_SOURCE": "did:web:${{ acme-id.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}",
        "FOXXI_ADMIN_WEB_ID": "https://${{ acme-id.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}/users/admin/profile/card#me",
        "FOXXI_LEARNING_ENGINEER_WEB_IDS": "https://${{ acme-id.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}/users/le/profile/card#me",
        "FOXXI_DASHBOARD_ORIGIN": "https://${{ foxxi-dashboard.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }},https://${{ foxxi-microsite.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }},https://${{ foxxi-scorm-player.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}",
        "FOXXI_AUDIENCE": "both",
        "FOXXI_TENANT_PROFILE_NAME": "Acme Training L&D",
        "FOXXI_REQUIRE_AUTH": "true",
        "FOXXI_LRS_BACKEND": "memory",
        "FOXXI_AGENTIC_RATE_LIMIT_PER_IP": "40",
        "MANIFEST_APPEND_ONLY_ENABLED": "false"
      },
      "secretEnv": [
        { "key": "FOXXI_RELAY_TRUST_SECRET", "azure": { "app": "interego-relay", "secret": "foxxi-relay-trust-secret" } },
        { "key": "FOXXI_ADMIN_KEY_SEED", "azure": { "app": "interego-foxxi-bridge", "secret": "foxxi-admin-key-seed" } },
        { "key": "FOXXI_ISSUER_KEY_SEED", "azure": { "app": "interego-foxxi-bridge", "secret": "foxxi-issuer-key-seed" } },
        { "key": "FOXXI_BRIDGE_PRIVATE_KEY", "azure": { "app": "interego-foxxi-bridge", "secret": "foxxi-bridge-private-key" } },
        { "key": "FOXXI_POD_WRITE_SECRET", "azure": { "app": "interego-foxxi-bridge", "secret": "foxxi-pod-write-secret" }, "never_echo": true },
        { "key": "FOXXI_LLM_API_KEY", "azure": { "app": "interego-foxxi-bridge", "secret": "foxxi-llm-api-key" } },
        { "key": "FOXXI_LRS_BASIC_AUTH_PAIRS", "azure": { "app": "interego-foxxi-bridge", "secret": "foxxi-lrs-basic-auth-pairs" }, "optional": true },
        { "key": "FOXXI_LANDING_PIN_SECRET", "azure": { "app": "interego-foxxi-bridge", "secret": "foxxi-landing-pin" }, "optional": true }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "bridge",
      "image": "interego-bridge:pedersen1",
      "port": 6050,
      "public": true,
      "env": {
        "PORT": "6050",
        "INTEREGO_DEFAULT_AGENT_DID": "did:web:interego-demo",
        "BRIDGE_DEPLOYMENT_URL": "https://${{ bridge.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "dashboard",
      "image": "interego-dashboard:69f84236ffffd69f6f68582cbf9bea253ef02d87",
      "port": 4000,
      "public": true,
      "env": {
        "CSS_URL": "https://${{ css-gate.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}/",
        "IDENTITY_URL": "https://${{ identity.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}",
        "RELAY_URL": "https://${{ relay.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}",
        "PUBLIC_RELAY_URL": "https://${{ relay.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}",
        "PUBLIC_BASE_URL": "https://${{ dashboard.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "pgsl-browser",
      "image": "interego-pgsl-browser:69f84236ffffd69f6f68582cbf9bea253ef02d87",
      "port": 5000,
      "public": true,
      "env": {
        "CSS_URL": "http://css.railway.internal:3456/",
        "POD_NAME": "markj",
        "CLEAN": "1",
        "PUBLIC_BASE_URL": "https://${{ pgsl-browser.RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN }}"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "microsite",
      "image": "interego-microsite:pedersen1",
      "port": 8080,
      "public": true,
      "env": {}
    },
    {
      "name": "main",
      "image": "interego-main:dcef885bf558bdea4b85b649e634d6aba3a59386",
      "port": 8080,
      "public": true,
      "env": {}
    },
    {
      "name": "acme-id",
      "image": "interego-acme-id:dcef885bf558bdea4b85b649e634d6aba3a59386",
      "port": 8080,
      "public": true,
      "env": {}
    },
    {
      "name": "foxxi-dashboard",
      "image": "interego-foxxi-dashboard:dcef885bf558bdea4b85b649e634d6aba3a59386",
      "port": 8080,
      "public": true,
      "env": {}
    },
    {
      "name": "foxxi-microsite",
      "image": "interego-foxxi-microsite:dcef885bf558bdea4b85b649e634d6aba3a59386",
      "port": 8080,
      "public": true,
      "env": {}
    },
    {
      "name": "foxxi-scorm-player",
      "image": "interego-foxxi-scorm-player:dcef885bf558bdea4b85b649e634d6aba3a59386",
      "port": 8080,
      "public": true,
      "env": {}
    }
  ],
  "post_deploy_notes": [
    "WEBAUTHN CAVEAT (Railway subdomains): *.up.railway.app is on the Public Suffix List, so a WebAuthn RP-ID cannot span two different railway.app subdomains. Passkey login works on identity's OWN subdomain; the cross-origin relay passkey ceremony (Azure's WEBAUTHN_RP_ORIGINS included the relay origin) will NOT validate here. Fixed by moving to a custom domain (identity.interego.xwisee.com + relay.interego.xwisee.com share the registrable domain). Acceptable for a trial.",
    "Fresh Postgres = clean slate: no pods/OAuth clients/ontologies carried over. Services bootstrap on first use; re-connect the claude.ai connector (new relay URL) and re-register passkeys. To instead preserve Azure data, pg_dump pgsl_prod per deploy/self-host/MIGRATION.md (adds the CSS base-URL re-key step).",
    "did:web:acme-id host: did:web resolves acme-id's Railway subdomain over public HTTPS to /.well-known/did.json — confirm the acme-id static image serves that path (it did on Azure).",
    "Enable Railway Cost Control / a usage cap on the project — Railway has no default spend cap and this is measured billing."
  ]
}
